Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.39,0:01:02.35,Main,,0,0,0,,[YOKO] It's not because nobody\Nelse was willing to eat with me,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.44,0:01:03.35,Main,,0,0,0,,all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.44,0:01:04.69,Main,,0,0,0,,[FUTABA]\NWe didn't think it was.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.77,0:01:06.19,Main,,0,0,0,,Wait, hold on. Do you not\Nhave any friends at all?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.27,0:01:07.65,Main,,0,0,0,,[YOKO]\NAre you always this direct?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.73,0:01:09.19,Main,,0,0,0,,The poor thing was\Ncrying pretty hard
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.28,0:01:10.44,Main,,0,0,0,,by the time it was over, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.53,0:01:12.49,Main,,0,0,0,,I wonder if it was\Nsomething I said.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.94,0:01:53.03,Main,,0,0,0,,[STUDENT 1A]\NI'm starving!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.11,0:01:54.57,Main,,0,0,0,,Can we eat already?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.74,0:01:57.08,Main,,0,0,0,,[STUDENT 1B]\NSorry I'm late!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.62,0:02:03.12,Main,,0,0,0,,[STUDENT 1E]\NI swear, it's true!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.21,0:02:06.08,Main,,0,0,0,,[STUDENTS laughing]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.17,0:02:07.08,Main,,0,0,0,,[STUDENT 1H]\NDid he really say that?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.17,0:02:09.00,Main,,0,0,0,,[STUDENT 1I]\NYep, word for word!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.09,0:02:10.00,Main,,0,0,0,,[STUDENT 1H]\NWow, that's hilarious!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.09,0:02:11.63,Main,,0,0,0,,What'd you tell him?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.65,0:02:36.57,Main,,0,0,0,,[HAYAMA]\NOh, no, I don't mind at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.66,0:02:39.41,Main,,0,0,0,,I just want to do the best\NI can as class representative.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.49,0:02:41.95,Main,,0,0,0,,[STUDENTS chattering]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.79,0:02:46.00,Main,,0,0,0,,[STUDENT 1M]\NSlow down. Wait for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.08,0:02:48.04,Main,,0,0,0,,[STUDENT 1L]\NC'mon, just hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.79,0:02:49.75,Main,,0,0,0,,[HAYAMA]\NHuh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.67,0:02:54.05,Main,,0,0,0,,[CAT meows]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.13,0:02:57.13,Main,,0,0,0,,[HAYAMA squeals]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.22,0:02:58.80,Main,,0,0,0,,[FUTABA] Move, people!\NOut of the way!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.89,0:03:00.47,Main,,0,0,0,,Whoops, sorry! Coming through!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.56,0:03:01.72,Main,,0,0,0,,Ugh! I'm so hungry!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.81,0:03:04.14,Main,,0,0,0,,If I don't eat soon,\NI'm gonna pass out.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.22,0:03:06.10,Main,,0,0,0,,And then I'll miss\Nmy next class!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.19,0:03:09.61,Main,,0,0,0,,[laughs] I'll just\Nhave to get creative.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.69,0:03:12.40,Main,,0,0,0,,There has gotta be a shortcut\Naround here I can take.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.03,0:03:16.57,Main,,0,0,0,,[HAYAMA laughing]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.58,0:03:27.83,Main,,0,0,0,,[FUTABA, HAYAMA gasp]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.63,0:03:37.38,Main,,0,0,0,,Excuse you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.51,0:03:45.93,Main,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey, hey!\NWhat are those you're eating?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.02,0:03:47.73,Main,,0,0,0,,Well, what do they look like?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.81,0:03:49.60,Main,,0,0,0,,These are bread crusts,\Nthank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.15,0:03:55.57,Main,,0,0,0,,[HAYAMA]\NWow, pig out much?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.65,0:03:57.15,Main,,0,0,0,,That's a lot of food!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.24,0:03:58.45,Main,,0,0,0,,[FUTABA]\NIt's not that much!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.53,0:04:00.28,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm actually being kind\Nof restrained today.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.37,0:04:01.74,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.24,0:04:05.25,Main,,0,0,0,,[FUTABA] Personally, I wonder\Nhow you can eat so little.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.33,0:04:07.54,Main,,0,0,0,,Is that really enough to keep\Nyou going all day long?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.62,0:04:10.21,Main,,0,0,0,,[HAYAMA] My body is just\Nmore efficient than yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.29,0:04:12.54,Main,,0,0,0,,I don't need all this.\NDo you want some?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.63,0:04:14.55,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I do! Woo-hoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.63,0:04:16.05,Main,,0,0,0,,You can have some too,\Nif you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.13,0:04:19.05,Main,,0,0,0,,What's the matter with you?\NDon't you have any manners?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.13,0:04:22.01,Main,,0,0,0,,I don't recall asking either\Nof you to join me for lunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.10,0:04:24.18,Main,,0,0,0,,Honestly, how rude!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.26,0:04:26.31,Main,,0,0,0,,Ah! That was amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.39,0:04:27.77,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, come on,\Nsay it again!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.85,0:04:31.40,Main,,0,0,0,,Please? You sound like\Na perfect little rich girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.48,0:04:32.94,Main,,0,0,0,,[FUTABA laughing]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.02,0:04:35.98,Main,,0,0,0,,Easy, now.\NPractice restraint, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.07,0:04:37.19,Main,,0,0,0,,[YOKO]\NAre you joking?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.28,0:04:38.61,Main,,0,0,0,,I don't even know how\Nto respond to that!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.69,0:04:40.28,Main,,0,0,0,,Guess we are being rude.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.36,0:04:43.03,Main,,0,0,0,,We haven't even introduced\Nourselves yet, have we?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.12,0:04:44.58,Main,,0,0,0,,My name is Hayama.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.66,0:04:47.50,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm doing Class 3 the favor\Nof being their representative.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.58,0:04:49.83,Main,,0,0,0,,Is that so? Lucky them.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.91,0:04:53.21,Main,,0,0,0,,And this is Futaba Odagiri,\NClass 3's glutton.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.29,0:04:54.75,Main,,0,0,0,,How's it goin'?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.38,0:04:57.76,Main,,0,0,0,,Well it's a pleasure\Nto meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.84,0:05:00.18,Main,,0,0,0,,My name is Yoko Nishikawa,\Nand I'm in Class 2.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.26,0:05:01.22,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah, we know.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.30,0:05:02.89,Main,,0,0,0,,Everyone here does.\NYou're famous.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.97,0:05:05.26,Main,,0,0,0,,[YOKO gasps]\NFamous?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.35,0:05:07.97,Main,,0,0,0,,So... I may have told someone to\Nkeep their filthy hands off me,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.06,0:05:09.48,Main,,0,0,0,,but last I checked\Nit wasn't a crime
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.56,0:05:10.98,Main,,0,0,0,,to value one's personal space!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.06,0:05:13.36,Main,,0,0,0,,Actually, that's the first time\NI've heard this story.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.44,0:05:14.36,Main,,0,0,0,,And however it looks,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.44,0:05:15.90,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm eating alone\Nbecause I want to.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.98,0:05:18.07,Main,,0,0,0,,It's not because nobody else\Nwas willing to eat with me,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.15,0:05:18.94,Main,,0,0,0,,all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.03,0:05:20.61,Main,,0,0,0,,Okay. We didn't think it was.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.69,0:05:21.65,Main,,0,0,0,,Wait, hold on.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.74,0:05:22.95,Main,,0,0,0,,Do you not have\Nany friends at all?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.03,0:05:25.20,Main,,0,0,0,,[YOKO]\NAre you always this direct?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.28,0:05:27.62,Main,,0,0,0,,I don't have much in common\Nwith the other students.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.70,0:05:29.20,Main,,0,0,0,,We're just too different.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.29,0:05:32.54,Main,,0,0,0,,How can I talk to anybody if I\Ndon't know what to talk about?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.62,0:05:34.33,Main,,0,0,0,,[laughs] It can't be that hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.42,0:05:35.83,Main,,0,0,0,,We're talking\Njust fine right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.92,0:05:37.09,Main,,0,0,0,,[FUTABA]\NUh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.06,0:05:56.36,Main,,0,0,0,,That breeze...\NThis is really great.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.44,0:05:59.57,Main,,0,0,0,,I'd forgotten how lovely\Nit can be to eat outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.07,0:06:02.15,Main,,0,0,0,,Well, maybe--
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.24,0:06:04.24,Main,,0,0,0,,--[bell rings]\N--Oh, there goes the bell.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.32,0:06:05.41,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.49,0:06:10.54,Main,,0,0,0,,[FUTABA]\NOkay, all done!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.62,0:06:12.62,Main,,0,0,0,,See you around, Yoko!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.71,0:06:13.96,Main,,0,0,0,,[HAYAMA]\NCatch you later!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.04,0:06:15.79,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh. Yeah. All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.88,0:06:18.13,Main,,0,0,0,,Hey, just so you know,\Nbread crusts are really yummy
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.21,0:06:20.71,Main,,0,0,0,,when you deep fry 'em and\Nsprinkle some sugar on top.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.80,0:06:22.38,Main,,0,0,0,,You just fry them in oil?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.46,0:06:23.88,Main,,0,0,0,,And add sugar?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.97,0:06:25.09,Main,,0,0,0,,I never thought of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.18,0:06:26.30,Main,,0,0,0,,Could you write\Ndown the recipe--
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.39,0:06:27.89,Main,,0,0,0,,[FUTABA]\NSorry, we gotta get going!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.97,0:06:31.14,Main,,0,0,0,,[HAYAMA] Our teacher gets super\Nangry whenever people are late!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.06,0:06:39.61,Main,,0,0,0,,--English is next.\N--[STUDENT 1T] Yup.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.69,0:06:42.53,Main,,0,0,0,,How was the homework?\NDid you get it done?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.61,0:06:44.65,Main,,0,0,0,,[YOKO]\NThose girls were so strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.74,0:06:46.74,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm not sure what\Nto make of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.82,0:06:48.12,Main,,0,0,0,,But still...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.33,0:06:54.91,Main,,0,0,0,,They were nice enough\Nin their own way, I suppose.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.00,0:06:57.42,Main,,0,0,0,,And that was the first time\NI haven't eaten lunch alone
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.50,0:06:59.59,Main,,0,0,0,,since I came to this school.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.71,0:07:04.17,Main,,0,0,0,,[YOKO]\NClass 3. So this is theirs.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.65,0:07:28.20,Main,,0,0,0,,I could barely\Nkeep my eyes open.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.28,0:07:29.57,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I hear you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.75,0:07:35.45,Main,,0,0,0,,[STUDENT 1W]\NIs that Nishikawa?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.25,0:07:39.83,Main,,0,0,0,,[STUDENT 1V]\NWhat's wrong with her?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.18,0:07:52.10,Main,,0,0,0,,[YOKO sighs] I'm so glad I\Nmade it before the sale ended.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.18,0:07:53.64,Main,,0,0,0,,Look at all this food!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.31,0:07:59.65,Main,,0,0,0,,Hey. Just so you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.73,0:08:01.52,Main,,0,0,0,,bread crusts are really yummy\Nwhen you deep fry them
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.61,0:08:03.48,Main,,0,0,0,,and sprinkle some sugar on top.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.32,0:08:08.53,Main,,0,0,0,,[YOKO]\NLet's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.61,0:08:12.12,Main,,0,0,0,,I'll need oil, and\Nhopefully I have some sugar.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.20,0:08:15.91,Main,,0,0,0,,[bell ringing]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.00,0:08:17.08,Main,,0,0,0,,[FUTABA]\NFinally, lunchtime!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.16,0:08:18.75,Main,,0,0,0,,I thought I was gonna starve!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.92,0:08:21.08,Main,,0,0,0,,Watch yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.17,0:08:22.96,Main,,0,0,0,,I think being class rep\Nis going to your head.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.04,0:08:25.42,Main,,0,0,0,,Sorry, Nishiyama.\NI don't know what you mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.50,0:08:26.67,Main,,0,0,0,,Yes, you do.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.76,0:08:28.22,Main,,0,0,0,,Or did you forget about\Nhow you badmouthed Kondo
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.30,0:08:29.38,Main,,0,0,0,,to the teacher yesterday?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.47,0:08:31.01,Main,,0,0,0,,There must be\Na misunderstanding.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.09,0:08:33.18,Main,,0,0,0,,All I did was deliver\Nthe printouts he wanted.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.26,0:08:35.47,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm not exactly sure why\NKondo didn't do it,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.56,0:08:37.77,Main,,0,0,0,,since she was the one on duty.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.35,0:08:41.06,Main,,0,0,0,,[laughs nervously]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.90,0:08:44.40,Main,,0,0,0,,Well... that doesn't matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.48,0:08:47.11,Main,,0,0,0,,I still think we should settle\Nthis with a little private chat.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.19,0:08:48.70,Main,,0,0,0,,Follow me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.78,0:08:50.24,Main,,0,0,0,,[HAYAMA]\NSure, if that's what you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.32,0:08:51.70,Main,,0,0,0,,Try not to be\Ntoo hard on her.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.78,0:08:54.62,Main,,0,0,0,,Whatever. I don't take\Norders from you, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.70,0:08:56.33,Main,,0,0,0,,[FUTABA] Um... I was\Nactually talking to Hayama,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.41,0:08:57.50,Main,,0,0,0,,but never mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.58,0:08:58.83,Main,,0,0,0,,[HAYAMA laughs]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.12,0:09:02.50,Main,,0,0,0,,[YOKO]\NIt was a bit of a challenge,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.58,0:09:04.04,Main,,0,0,0,,but I hope they like it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.54,0:09:06.67,Main,,0,0,0,,[YOKO shrieks]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.72,0:09:15.93,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm here! And I\Nbrought a surprise.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.32,0:09:29.49,Main,,0,0,0,,Well, it's not like we\Nactually agreed to meet again.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.57,0:09:31.65,Main,,0,0,0,,And now I can go back\Nto enjoying a solitary meal,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.74,0:09:33.45,Main,,0,0,0,,just like before.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.50,0:09:41.54,Main,,0,0,0,,I like it this way. Really.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.62,0:09:43.46,Main,,0,0,0,,[rustling]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.25,0:09:47.80,Main,,0,0,0,,[FUTABA]\NThat was a stupid way to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.88,0:09:48.88,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm all scratched up!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.96,0:09:51.17,Main,,0,0,0,,What a surprise. It's you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.26,0:09:53.68,Main,,0,0,0,,You're the one who\Ninsisted we take a shortcut.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.76,0:09:56.64,Main,,0,0,0,,Well I didn't want to keep\NYoko waiting for too long.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.72,0:09:58.85,Main,,0,0,0,,I thought you'd\Nforgotten about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.93,0:10:00.35,Main,,0,0,0,,[FUTABA]\NDid you have to wait long?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.43,0:10:01.98,Main,,0,0,0,,[HAYAMA]\NI'm so sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.06,0:10:03.73,Main,,0,0,0,,Yes. It's been five minutes!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.81,0:10:05.52,Main,,0,0,0,,I hope you have a valid excuse!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.61,0:10:06.90,Main,,0,0,0,,I do, actually.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.98,0:10:09.02,Main,,0,0,0,,Someone decided they\Nwanted to pick a fight with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.11,0:10:10.90,Main,,0,0,0,,What? Oh no!\NAre you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.99,0:10:11.99,Main,,0,0,0,,Yep!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.07,0:10:13.28,Main,,0,0,0,,The poor thing was\Ncrying pretty hard
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.36,0:10:14.53,Main,,0,0,0,,by the time it was over though.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.61,0:10:17.33,Main,,0,0,0,,I wonder if it\Nwas something I said.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.41,0:10:18.20,Main,,0,0,0,,[FUTABA]\NTrust me on this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.28,0:10:20.12,Main,,0,0,0,,It's best not to ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.20,0:10:22.12,Main,,0,0,0,,[rustling]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.21,0:10:27.84,Main,,0,0,0,,Huh? Who's in there?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.92,0:10:29.50,Main,,0,0,0,,I bet it's some freaky stalker.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.59,0:10:31.30,Main,,0,0,0,,They go around hiding\Nin bushes, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.38,0:10:33.17,Main,,0,0,0,,[YAMAJI yells]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.26,0:10:34.97,Main,,0,0,0,,[ALL scream]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.05,0:10:36.72,Main,,0,0,0,,Yamaji!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.80,0:10:38.43,Main,,0,0,0,,[HAYAMA]\NYou know this guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.51,0:10:41.10,Main,,0,0,0,,[YOKO]\NI do. He's my former servant.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.18,0:10:43.98,Main,,0,0,0,,[YAMAJI] Please,\Nforgive me for intruding!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.06,0:10:44.81,Main,,0,0,0,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.89,0:10:46.52,Main,,0,0,0,,Calm down. Explain yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.60,0:10:49.52,Main,,0,0,0,,[YAMAJI] I'm sorry, but I had to\Nknow for sure what I'd seen.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.61,0:10:51.74,Main,,0,0,0,,Was yesterday's encounter\Nfleeting or would it endure?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.82,0:10:54.03,Main,,0,0,0,,So you were in the\Nbushes yesterday too?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.11,0:10:57.24,Main,,0,0,0,,Yes, and I admit I was\Nshocked by what I saw.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.32,0:10:59.03,Main,,0,0,0,,I was convinced that\Nit would take a miracle
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.12,0:11:00.95,Main,,0,0,0,,for Miss Yoko to make friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.04,0:11:03.29,Main,,0,0,0,,Hey, what's that\Nsupposed to mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.37,0:11:05.12,Main,,0,0,0,,[YAMAJI] With your family\Ncompany's bankruptcy,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.21,0:11:08.25,Main,,0,0,0,,you're a shadow of the rich\Nyoung lady you once were!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.34,0:11:10.46,Main,,0,0,0,,Even so, your upbringing\Nmakes it difficult
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.54,0:11:12.30,Main,,0,0,0,,for you to forsake the\Nupper-class attitudes
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.38,0:11:13.84,Main,,0,0,0,,you've embraced all your life.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.92,0:11:15.76,Main,,0,0,0,,So for you to befriend\Nthe everyday folk
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.84,0:11:17.30,Main,,0,0,0,,who attend your new school...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.38,0:11:19.14,Main,,0,0,0,,It must surely be a miracle!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.22,0:11:20.14,Main,,0,0,0,,Wow...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.22,0:11:21.51,Main,,0,0,0,,It's not like that at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.60,0:11:23.73,Main,,0,0,0,,Yamaji, you're\Nobviously exaggerating!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.81,0:11:24.98,Main,,0,0,0,,[YAMAJI]\NI beg you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.06,0:11:27.39,Main,,0,0,0,,Look after Miss Yoko as\Nshe starts her new life!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.48,0:11:29.65,Main,,0,0,0,,Be her true friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.58,0:11:43.87,Main,,0,0,0,,Boy, that was fascinating!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.95,0:11:44.95,Main,,0,0,0,,Should we eat?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.04,0:11:45.66,Main,,0,0,0,,But I...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.75,0:11:46.96,Main,,0,0,0,,You know I'm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.04,0:11:48.21,Main,,0,0,0,,Listen, I can explain.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.29,0:11:50.29,Main,,0,0,0,,What Yamaji said\Nmay be partially true.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.38,0:11:51.88,Main,,0,0,0,,[HAYAMA]\NIt's so nice out today.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.96,0:11:55.05,Main,,0,0,0,,Eating on the grass...\NSurrounded by nature.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.26,0:11:57.76,Main,,0,0,0,,Are you ignoring me?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.84,0:11:59.22,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh. I was right!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.30,0:12:01.18,Main,,0,0,0,,I knew you would never really\Nbe able to make friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.26,0:12:04.06,Main,,0,0,0,,--That's enough, Yamaji!\N--I'm sorry. But... It's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.14,0:12:05.31,Main,,0,0,0,,[HAYAMA laughs]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.61,0:12:14.61,Main,,0,0,0,,[STUDENTS chattering]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.53,0:12:17.65,Main,,0,0,0,,[YOKO]\NHonestly!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.74,0:12:19.91,Main,,0,0,0,,Must they insist on\Nmaking all this noise?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.99,0:12:22.16,Main,,0,0,0,,I mean, we are here\Nto learn, aren't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.24,0:12:24.74,Main,,0,0,0,,But it's impossible with\Nall this constant chatter.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.83,0:12:26.41,Main,,0,0,0,,I couldn't imagine\Ntrying to make friends
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.50,0:12:27.79,Main,,0,0,0,,with girls like these.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.87,0:12:29.46,Main,,0,0,0,,So loud and unladylike.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.54,0:12:32.42,Main,,0,0,0,,[FUTABA]\NHey, over here, Yoko!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.50,0:12:33.67,Main,,0,0,0,,What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.75,0:12:36.76,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, hi!\NWhat are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.84,0:12:39.38,Main,,0,0,0,,Ugh! Think we could\Ntake it down a notch?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.38,0:12:42.22,Main,,0,0,0,,[YOKO] What did you\Nwant to talk to me about?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.30,0:12:43.26,Main,,0,0,0,,I need a favor.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.35,0:12:45.14,Main,,0,0,0,,I sorta left my\Nmath book at home.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.22,0:12:47.39,Main,,0,0,0,,Maybe you could\Nlet me borrow yours?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.48,0:12:48.48,Main,,0,0,0,,I do wish I could help,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.56,0:12:50.39,Main,,0,0,0,,but my class doesn't\Nhave math today,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.48,0:12:51.48,Main,,0,0,0,,so I didn't bring it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.56,0:12:54.57,Main,,0,0,0,,Aw, you didn't?\NReally? That's too bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.65,0:12:57.24,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry! Forgive me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.32,0:12:59.36,Main,,0,0,0,,I promise, if my means\Nweren't so badly diminished,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.45,0:13:01.66,Main,,0,0,0,,I would have a servant\Nfetch it for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.74,0:13:04.66,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, no, it's really\Nnot that big a deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.91,0:13:09.75,Main,,0,0,0,,Anyway, see you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.84,0:13:16.09,Main,,0,0,0,,[FUTABA]\NLet's eat! I'm wasting away.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.17,0:13:18.59,Main,,0,0,0,,I apologize for not being\Nable to help you earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.67,0:13:20.34,Main,,0,0,0,,Are you talking\Nabout the textbook?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.42,0:13:23.35,Main,,0,0,0,,No, no! It's my bad for\Nnot bringing it with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.43,0:13:24.93,Main,,0,0,0,,Not having her book\Nisn't going to make
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.01,0:13:26.85,Main,,0,0,0,,that big of a difference\Nto Little Miss ADD
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.93,0:13:28.27,Main,,0,0,0,,over here anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.35,0:13:30.60,Main,,0,0,0,,Exactly! Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.77,0:13:33.19,Main,,0,0,0,,[FUTABA] Do you realize\Nwhen you're being mean,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.27,0:13:35.44,Main,,0,0,0,,or do you just talk\Nbefore you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.52,0:13:37.69,Main,,0,0,0,,[HAYAMA] I was just\Ntelling the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.78,0:13:39.40,Main,,0,0,0,,Forget it. I don't even care.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.49,0:13:41.24,Main,,0,0,0,,Right now I just wanna eat!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.70,0:13:46.53,Main,,0,0,0,,Uh... what in the\Nworld are you eating?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.62,0:13:48.79,Main,,0,0,0,,You really don't know?\NThis is called bread.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.87,0:13:50.16,Main,,0,0,0,,I know what bread is.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.25,0:13:52.50,Main,,0,0,0,,What I don't get is why\Nyou're eating a whole loaf.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.58,0:13:54.79,Main,,0,0,0,,Well, it's filling, and it's\Neasier than making a sandwich.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.88,0:13:57.63,Main,,0,0,0,,Do you realize when\Nyou sound like an idiot?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.71,0:13:58.80,Main,,0,0,0,,What about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.88,0:14:00.67,Main,,0,0,0,,Are you having bread\Ncrusts again today?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.76,0:14:03.26,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah! You can get\Nso many of them
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.34,0:14:04.64,Main,,0,0,0,,for such little money!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.72,0:14:06.26,Main,,0,0,0,,When I first saw\Nthese in the store,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.35,0:14:08.39,Main,,0,0,0,,I thought it was\Ntoo good to be true.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.47,0:14:10.43,Main,,0,0,0,,[FUTABA] That doesn't really\Nmake for a balanced lunch,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.52,0:14:11.93,Main,,0,0,0,,though.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.02,0:14:14.31,Main,,0,0,0,,Fortunately, I discovered\Nsomething to solve that problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.36,0:14:22.20,Main,,0,0,0,,There, you see?\NIt's perfectly nutritious!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.28,0:14:23.57,Main,,0,0,0,,[FUTABA]\NUm, not exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.65,0:14:26.45,Main,,0,0,0,,[sobbing]
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.53,0:14:28.95,Main,,0,0,0,,[YAMAJI crying]\NMy poor Miss Yoko!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.03,0:14:30.83,Main,,0,0,0,,You've fallen so far!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.91,0:14:31.87,Main,,0,0,0,,Gaaah!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.96,0:14:33.41,Main,,0,0,0,,Yamaji?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.50,0:14:35.04,Main,,0,0,0,,You know if you keep trespassing\Non school grounds like this
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.13,0:14:36.46,Main,,0,0,0,,I'll have to call the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.54,0:14:38.71,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, I'm not trespassing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.79,0:14:40.84,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm in charge of refilling\Nthe vending machines.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.92,0:14:42.01,Main,,0,0,0,,It's a side job.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.09,0:14:43.84,Main,,0,0,0,,[HAYAMA] Never mind, then.\NIt's all good.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.92,0:14:45.97,Main,,0,0,0,,This guy's a stalker!\NHow is it "all good?"
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.05,0:14:47.64,Main,,0,0,0,,That is absolutely unfair!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.72,0:14:49.43,Main,,0,0,0,,The only thing I'm doing\Nis watching quietly
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.51,0:14:50.93,Main,,0,0,0,,from the shadows\Nwithout anybody knowing,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.02,0:14:52.35,Main,,0,0,0,,and you're calling\Nme a stalker?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.43,0:14:54.18,Main,,0,0,0,,[FUTABA]\NThat's basically the definition!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.27,0:14:55.56,Main,,0,0,0,,It's completely innocent.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.64,0:14:57.81,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm only concerned about\NMiss Yoko's welfare.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.90,0:14:59.32,Main,,0,0,0,,My grandfather had this job.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.40,0:15:01.36,Main,,0,0,0,,When he passed away,\NI took over for him,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.44,0:15:03.28,Main,,0,0,0,,and then the company\Nwent bankrupt.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.36,0:15:06.41,Main,,0,0,0,,So taking care of her\Nis my family's legacy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.49,0:15:08.32,Main,,0,0,0,,I can't help but worry how\Nshe'll make the adjustment
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.41,0:15:10.49,Main,,0,0,0,,to being among the common folk.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.58,0:15:13.04,Main,,0,0,0,,She has such an\Nexplosive temper, you see.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.12,0:15:15.62,Main,,0,0,0,,If everything doesn't go exactly\Nthe way she wants them to,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.71,0:15:16.17,Main,,0,0,0,,terrible things--
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.25,0:15:18.46,Main,,0,0,0,,That's enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.54,0:15:20.63,Main,,0,0,0,,[YAMAJI]\NHere, I want you to have these.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.71,0:15:22.42,Main,,0,0,0,,They're clearance goods\Nfrom the vending machines.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.50,0:15:24.51,Main,,0,0,0,,Expired, but only barely!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.59,0:15:26.30,Main,,0,0,0,,But... I don't need this.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.38,0:15:27.51,Main,,0,0,0,,Whoops.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.59,0:15:28.55,Main,,0,0,0,,I think I'm gonna be\Nlate for my next job.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.64,0:15:30.05,Main,,0,0,0,,I'll see you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.68,0:15:36.06,Main,,0,0,0,,[FUTABA] It seems like\Nit would be way easier
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.14,0:15:38.02,Main,,0,0,0,,to just give you cash,\Ndon'tcha think?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.10,0:15:39.52,Main,,0,0,0,,Something tells me\Nthat he doesn't have
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.61,0:15:40.86,Main,,0,0,0,,a lot of money to spare.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.94,0:15:43.19,Main,,0,0,0,,Truly, I don't know\Nwhat's the matter with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.28,0:15:45.86,Main,,0,0,0,,Does he really think\NI want all this stuff?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.95,0:15:48.11,Main,,0,0,0,,Well, he couldn't be\Nmore wrong about that!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.20,0:15:50.41,Main,,0,0,0,,Hey, you're kinda glowing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.49,0:15:52.53,Main,,0,0,0,,[YOKO] Every time I start\Nto feel more at ease,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.62,0:15:54.83,Main,,0,0,0,,Yamaji shows up\Nand humiliates me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.91,0:15:56.75,Main,,0,0,0,,I've finally made\Nsome friends here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.83,0:15:59.42,Main,,0,0,0,,I don't want anything\Nto scare them away!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.09,0:16:03.50,Main,,0,0,0,,[YAMAJI]\NHere you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.59,0:16:05.42,Main,,0,0,0,,Today's expired\Nvending machine goods.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.51,0:16:06.72,Main,,0,0,0,,They're all yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.30,0:16:10.76,Main,,0,0,0,,[YOKO] Couldn't he at least find\Na more private time to do this?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.31,0:16:15.73,Main,,0,0,0,,Fine! If you insist,\NI'll take them
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.81,0:16:17.73,Main,,0,0,0,,Excellent. I'm off then. Bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.81,0:16:19.73,Main,,0,0,0,,[YOKO]\NStay calm, Yoko, stay calm.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.81,0:16:22.15,Main,,0,0,0,,No matter what you see,\Ndon't squeal with delight.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.23,0:16:24.23,Main,,0,0,0,,They'll think you\Nhave no self-control.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.32,0:16:27.74,Main,,0,0,0,,[YOKO squeals]\NDo you see that? It's cheese!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.82,0:16:28.95,Main,,0,0,0,,Wow, that's exciting.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.03,0:16:30.45,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm happy for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.53,0:16:32.70,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah, cheese is healthier\Nthan a lot of that other stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.87,0:16:36.33,Main,,0,0,0,,[HAYAMA]\NI've got a question.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.41,0:16:38.87,Main,,0,0,0,,If you had to eat one food every\Nday, what would you choose?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.96,0:16:39.79,Main,,0,0,0,,White rice.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.87,0:16:41.50,Main,,0,0,0,,I'd assumed you\Nwould say bread.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.58,0:16:43.96,Main,,0,0,0,,I guess I kinda consider\Nbread more like a snack.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.04,0:16:46.21,Main,,0,0,0,,Rice is good 'cause it goes\Nwith just about anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.30,0:16:48.47,Main,,0,0,0,,Then why don't you pack\Nsomething with rice?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.55,0:16:50.51,Main,,0,0,0,,I don't have enough time\Nfor that in the morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.59,0:16:52.05,Main,,0,0,0,,Okay, What's your favorite?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.14,0:16:53.76,Main,,0,0,0,,Me? Oh, that's easy!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.85,0:16:59.56,Main,,0,0,0,,I... love... mille-feuille!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.94,0:17:03.98,Main,,0,0,0,,[HAYAMA] Ugh! Fine!\NIt's salty fish paste.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.07,0:17:05.19,Main,,0,0,0,,You got a problem with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.28,0:17:06.40,Main,,0,0,0,,No. No problem at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.48,0:17:08.69,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh! Yeah, that\Nstuff is delicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.78,0:17:10.78,Main,,0,0,0,,It goes really well with rice!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.86,0:17:11.91,Main,,0,0,0,,What about you, Yoko?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.99,0:17:13.41,Main,,0,0,0,,I bet it's cheese.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.91,0:17:16.29,Main,,0,0,0,,[YOKO]\NI need to be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.37,0:17:18.58,Main,,0,0,0,,I have to choose an answer\Nthey won't think is strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.66,0:17:19.87,Main,,0,0,0,,Something pedestrian.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.96,0:17:22.83,Main,,0,0,0,,Something regular people like.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.92,0:17:24.42,Main,,0,0,0,,Flan's delicious,\Ndon't you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.50,0:17:25.59,Main,,0,0,0,,Ew, no way!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.67,0:17:27.38,Main,,0,0,0,,But flan would be\Ntotally gross with rice!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.46,0:17:28.88,Main,,0,0,0,,Does that matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.97,0:17:31.55,Main,,0,0,0,,[YOKO] Is that what\Nnormal people like?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.63,0:17:33.55,Main,,0,0,0,,Foods that pair well with rice?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.64,0:17:35.56,Main,,0,0,0,,I need to try a\Ndifferent answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.64,0:17:38.72,Main,,0,0,0,,Uh... pink codfish\Nflakes sure are tasty.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.81,0:17:40.48,Main,,0,0,0,,[FUTABA]\NCodfish flakes?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.02,0:17:43.69,Main,,0,0,0,,I know! Mayonnaise!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.77,0:17:45.69,Main,,0,0,0,,Well, at least that\Nsounds more like the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.77,0:17:46.86,Main,,0,0,0,,Don't take this the wrong way,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.94,0:17:48.44,Main,,0,0,0,,but are you sure\Nyou used to be rich?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.53,0:17:50.32,Main,,0,0,0,,Well, I uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.40,0:17:51.36,Main,,0,0,0,,[YOKO]\NIt's hopeless.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.45,0:17:53.28,Main,,0,0,0,,I can't seem to say\Nthe right thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.37,0:17:56.79,Main,,0,0,0,,What if they start to hate me?\NI'll have to eat alone again.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.24,0:18:02.25,Main,,0,0,0,,[rice cooker beeping]
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.79,0:18:06.96,Main,,0,0,0,,[YOKO] I shouldn't worry.\NIt'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.22,0:18:14.64,Main,,0,0,0,,[YOKO] After all,\NThey were impressed with
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.72,0:18:16.14,Main,,0,0,0,,the fried bread crusts.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.22,0:18:18.26,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm sure they'll like these too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.86,0:18:32.57,Main,,0,0,0,,Come on, ladies!\NAren't you ready for lunch?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.65,0:18:35.37,Main,,0,0,0,,I have a surprise for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.45,0:18:38.03,Main,,0,0,0,,Presenting my very\Nfirst batch of rice balls.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.12,0:18:39.79,Main,,0,0,0,,[BOTH]\NWhoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.87,0:18:41.75,Main,,0,0,0,,[FUTABA] I thought she lived\Non a diet of bread crusts.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.83,0:18:44.62,Main,,0,0,0,,Who knew all this time\NI've had hidden culinary skills?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.71,0:18:45.96,Main,,0,0,0,,I can't make 'em.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.04,0:18:47.84,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm impressed you were\Nable to learn so quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.92,0:18:49.88,Main,,0,0,0,,It was simple,\Nand there're plenty here,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.96,0:18:51.92,Main,,0,0,0,,so feel free to dig in!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.01,0:18:54.51,Main,,0,0,0,,Do you think she means\Nballs of just rice?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.59,0:18:56.34,Main,,0,0,0,,No. No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.35,0:19:00.22,Main,,0,0,0,,Those look like plain\Nballs of rice to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.31,0:19:02.02,Main,,0,0,0,,You mentioned yesterday\Nhow much you loved it,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.10,0:19:03.81,Main,,0,0,0,,so I thought these\Nwould be perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.89,0:19:05.94,Main,,0,0,0,,That's true.\NRice is my favorite.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.02,0:19:08.77,Main,,0,0,0,,What I like most about it\Nis how versatile it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.86,0:19:11.73,Main,,0,0,0,,Like how rice balls can have\Nso many different fillings.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.86,0:19:17.07,Main,,0,0,0,,I didn't realize they were\Nsupposed to have filling.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.16,0:19:18.24,Main,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.32,0:19:19.91,Main,,0,0,0,,I thought about adding\Nsalted fish paste,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.99,0:19:22.45,Main,,0,0,0,,since Hayama likes it so much,\Nbut it was expensive.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.54,0:19:24.04,Main,,0,0,0,,You were gonna do that\Njust for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.12,0:19:26.58,Main,,0,0,0,,That would have been an\Ninteresting choice, all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.67,0:19:28.13,Main,,0,0,0,,The trickiest part\Nabout making them
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.21,0:19:30.17,Main,,0,0,0,,is getting the\Nperfect salt level.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.25,0:19:32.01,Main,,0,0,0,,[YOKO gasps]\NThe salt!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.09,0:19:34.47,Main,,0,0,0,,I was afraid I'd\Nforgotten something!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.22,0:19:40.31,Main,,0,0,0,,[YOKO]\NOh no. I did it again.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.39,0:19:42.14,Main,,0,0,0,,I made a fool of myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.22,0:19:44.60,Main,,0,0,0,,I thought I was making\Nsomething really special.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.68,0:19:46.27,Main,,0,0,0,,Stupid Yoko.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.98,0:19:49.65,Main,,0,0,0,,[FUTABA]\NAre we gonna eat or not?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.65,0:19:56.24,Main,,0,0,0,,Thanks for cooking.\NThat was sweet of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.74,0:20:00.20,Main,,0,0,0,,[FUTABA]\NMind if I have another one?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.08,0:20:02.37,Main,,0,0,0,,You don't have to.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.45,0:20:05.87,Main,,0,0,0,,Please don't eat them\Njust to make me feel better.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.95,0:20:08.12,Main,,0,0,0,,Hey, I told you\Nrice is my favorite!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.63,0:20:13.42,Main,,0,0,0,,Well, in that case...\NHave as much as you want!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.30,0:20:16.30,Main,,0,0,0,,[stomach growls]
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.13,0:20:21.93,Main,,0,0,0,,[laughing]
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.01,0:20:23.01,Main,,0,0,0,,[FUTABA]\NCome on, Yoko!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.10,0:20:24.39,Main,,0,0,0,,It sounds like you\Nneed to eat, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.47,0:20:26.85,Main,,0,0,0,,[HAYAMA] Would you like one\Nof my Vienna sausages?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.93,0:20:28.73,Main,,0,0,0,,[YOKO] Thank you,\Nthat sounds wonderful!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.81,0:20:30.31,Main,,0,0,0,,[FUTABA] Just one more,\Nthen I'll stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.40,0:20:32.40,Main,,0,0,0,,[HAYAMA snorts, laughs]
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.15,0:20:36.90,Main,,0,0,0,,[YOKO] You don't have to\Ndo anything to thank me
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.99,0:20:38.90,Main,,0,0,0,,for cooking.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.99,0:20:41.74,Main,,0,0,0,,I was happy to do it.\NI wanted to.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.83,0:20:42.87,Main,,0,0,0,,Because we're friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.95,0:20:45.16,Main,,0,0,0,,Don't be so shy.\NNot around us.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.24,0:20:47.96,Main,,0,0,0,,Loosen up, since we're\Nfriends and all!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.17,0:20:53.25,Main,,0,0,0,,If it makes you feel better,\Nthey were free tickets.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.34,0:20:56.34,Main,,0,0,0,,I kinda have something of a hook\Nup for random stuff like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.42,0:20:57.55,Main,,0,0,0,,Here we are!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.97,0:21:00.59,Main,,0,0,0,,[YOKO]\NA bathhouse!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.35,0:21:08.18,Main,,0,0,0,,[ALL]\NAhh!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.27,0:21:10.39,Main,,0,0,0,,Nothing like a nice\Nhot bath to ease the mind
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.48,0:21:12.94,Main,,0,0,0,,and relax the body.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.02,0:21:16.90,Main,,0,0,0,,I hear ya.\NAnd it smells wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.98,0:21:18.74,Main,,0,0,0,,This is absolutely amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.82,0:21:21.20,Main,,0,0,0,,I can barely remember\Nthe last time I had a bath
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.28,0:21:23.49,Main,,0,0,0,,that was this luxurious!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.41,0:21:27.70,Main,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.79,0:21:29.20,Main,,0,0,0,,It must take a lot of\Nenergy to heat enough water
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.29,0:21:30.71,Main,,0,0,0,,for a bath this big.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.79,0:21:33.71,Main,,0,0,0,,I can't even imagine how high\Nthe utility bills must be!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.79,0:21:35.75,Main,,0,0,0,,Relax already!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.84,0:21:37.71,Main,,0,0,0,,[YOKO]\NI lost it a little. Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.80,0:21:39.80,Main,,0,0,0,,[HAYAMA, FUTABA laugh]
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.80,0:21:43.18,Main,,0,0,0,,[YAMAJI]\NA little spa time!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.26,0:21:45.35,Main,,0,0,0,,If that's not girl bonding,\Nthan I don't know what is!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.43,0:21:47.06,Main,,0,0,0,,I was worried, but\Nit looks like Miss Yoko
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.14,0:21:48.43,Main,,0,0,0,,will be okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.06,0:21:51.23,Main,,0,0,0,,I think it might be\Ntime for you to get out.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.31,0:21:53.40,Main,,0,0,0,,[YOKO] But it was so kind\Nof Hayama to bring me here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.48,0:21:54.48,Main,,0,0,0,,I don't want to waste it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.56,0:21:55.48,Main,,0,0,0,,Don't worry about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.57,0:21:56.98,Main,,0,0,0,,It was free, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.07,0:21:58.73,Main,,0,0,0,,I should stay an hour longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.82,0:22:01.36,Main,,0,0,0,,No. Maybe a whole day longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.45,0:22:03.20,Main,,0,0,0,,If you're not careful,\Nyou'll pass out!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.28,0:22:04.45,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.53,0:22:06.37,Main,,0,0,0,,You're gonna turn into\NYoko soup pretty soon!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.45,0:22:10.58,Main,,0,0,0,,Ahh... No, really I'm good.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.66,0:22:12.04,Main,,0,0,0,,[FUTABA, HAYAMA]\NYoko!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.89,0:23:51.51,Main,,0,0,0,,[YOKO] And so my\Ntumultuous school life began.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.60,0:23:54.10,Main,,0,0,0,,This new dog eat dog\Nworld is full of trials,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.18,0:23:56.35,Main,,0,0,0,,such as understanding\Nhow to spend break time!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.44,0:23:57.44,Main,,0,0,0,,But from now on...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.52,0:23:59.27,Main,,0,0,0,,I won't lunch alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.36,0:24:01.52,Main,,0,0,0,,[FUTABA] Shall we eat\Nindoors when it rains?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.61,0:24:02.65,Main,,0,0,0,,[YOKO]\NYes.
